Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.45,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.95,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.54,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.81,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現  夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.98,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.90,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.40,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.56,0:01:03.69,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.98,0:01:09.81,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.81,0:01:11.33,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.71,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.48,0:01:23.66,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.64,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.20,0:21:33.51,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.62,0:21:40.31,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.59,0:21:48.98,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.11,0:21:53.24,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.07,0:22:01.55,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.73,0:22:05.96,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.53,0:22:14.09,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.33,0:22:18.55,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.92,0:22:26.10,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.26,0:22:33.11,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.48,0:22:38.61,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.77,0:22:47.66,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.90,0:00:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的故事發生在高爾夫練習場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘊含殺機的漂亮擊球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.10,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高爾夫練習場殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.19,0:01:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.57,0:01:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看太勉強了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔哪會打高爾夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也說過他拿這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用運動器材的運動項目最沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一開始的時候拒絕不就好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔之所以開始碰高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.71,0:02:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為三天前那通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.63,0:02:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從日賣電視臺打來的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說慈善高爾夫大會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.43,0:02:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對高爾夫實在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.51,0:02:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沖野洋子小姐推薦我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐也會出席比賽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好那好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別看我這個樣子 打高爾夫是我最拿手的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且再怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算早上練習的優惠不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有必要六點半就到這兒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要拖我們兩個一起下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要好好打個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.88,0:02:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.17,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作前就應該有適當的運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.09,0:02:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託經理的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的健康狀況好的不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.93,0:03:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.82,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你肚子痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這傢伙真是掃興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗手間 早去早回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三振 打擊者出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球什麼時候才會飛到外野去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看別人打球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以妨礙別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理 這些給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會拍馬屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟那裏很危險你站到旁邊來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我站的這裏距離很遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理遠距離球桿的修理費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次得從零用金裏面出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎 那裏很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理今天的手氣真是順
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下星期日的歡送聯誼賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理一定可以得到優勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的這麼快就打完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個叔叔打球的速度本來就比大家快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還特地把一些球分給那個經理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍馬屁也拍得太明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.59,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是長距離球桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.94,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒打中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經二十次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快聯絡目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才發生了炸彈爆炸事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.61,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種特殊的味道好刺鼻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑色火藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個裏面就有一家醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己的手不是也受傷了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是沒什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我了 快送大久保去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一位死者是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五井電機的橘經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾位是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是課長安井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大久保 還有南智史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們全都是橘經理的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也同樣是商品開發部的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們常常到這個地方來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為公司距離這裏很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理今天是最後一次到這兒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就會升職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調到紐約去做分公司的社長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.71,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子所使用的是黑色火藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您到這邊來一下好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是長距離球桿頭的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外散落在這附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是高爾夫球的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再請您看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為 這個是雷管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.70,0:08:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈被安裝在高爾夫球裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用球桿打擊的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈就會因為撞擊的衝擊產生爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這裏的球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每顆上面是不是都有一條紅線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 上面都是藍線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 的確是藍線沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有一條線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個有紅色交叉雙線的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有安裝炸彈的記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.53,0:08:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場謀殺到底是針對橘經理他個人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一種不分物件的恐怖行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為 這名兇手的目的是在於謀殺經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為在這裏的三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我和大久保主任 還有安井課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有足夠讓我們殺害經理的仇恨存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼 南智史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.84,0:09:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.34,0:09:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的確都有充分的動機殺害經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.64,0:09:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿我來說好了 在這之前就曾經有三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新產品的創意被經理用他的名義提交上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.94,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.80,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道提過幾次的建議從來都沒有被接受過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟經理什麼問題也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.99,0:09:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安井課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用再說謊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家都心知肚明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.95,0:09:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最心愛的女朋友就被經理給搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.58,0:09:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把她甩了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理才開始跟她交往的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道到底是誰殺了橘經理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.81,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 從犯案的手法來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手把裝了炸彈的球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他的球事先混在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓被害人用球桿來撞擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 最有嫌疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是從領球機裏面把球拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再把球放進橘經理桶子裏的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.28,0:10:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是大久保叔叔了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南叔叔剛好到洗手間去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安井叔叔他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在自己的機器那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來 就是你下的毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.34,0:10:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小弟弟說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟南智史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天根本沒碰過經理的球桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把裝了炸彈的高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放進球桶裏的除了你沒有別人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你這話也不能這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南先生在案發的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.23,0:10:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確不在現場 所以沒有犯案的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是安井先生你可就不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才明明就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你一部份的球分給橘經理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 你也很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那顆裝了炸彈的高爾夫球裝進這個裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我把裝了炸彈的球裝進來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那個時候炸彈就爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.42,0:11:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定也會一起死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這個機器的構造來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後放進去的高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是最後一個出來的才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你就設計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比橘先生早把桶裏的球打完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.85,0:11:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了趕在裝有炸彈的球出來前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是三兩下就把球打完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.07,0:11:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人原本就有打得快的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.99,0:11:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧 大久保 南智史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈爆炸的時候 你當時究竟在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大久保先生也沒有任何嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為他和南先生都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們那個時候就在案發的現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會被炸彈的爆炸威力波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你確實是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候正在出口的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.35,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看到那顆用紅線做記號的裝了炸彈的高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就急急忙忙的跑去避難了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是去跟櫃檯訂咖啡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.82,0:12:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們經理每次打完球之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喜歡喝這裏的老闆娘親手沖的咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每次在他要打完的前十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會先去櫃檯拜託她開始準備咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是他說的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們這裏煮的是咖啡豆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們都希望客人提早告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.76,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當那個炸彈爆炸的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有你一個人剛好離開案發現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說這也未免太巧合了一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為兇手就是安井先生了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是兇手 真的不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安井先生 為了慎重起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請讓我們檢查你帶來的行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.90,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.70,0:13:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔的推理的確罕見的完全沒有矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果他就是真正的兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.72,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發現他的袋子裏有這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.97,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是最有力的鐵證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一那顆球沒有起作用的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就可以當做備份來使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這件案子非常的單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我名偵探毛利小五郎來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像吃早飯那麼輕而易舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也太單純了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是安井先生殺了橘經理的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是等著被抓嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…這裏面一定有什麼我們疏忽掉的細節才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼連我也沒有注意到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九號臺上的高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概又是叔叔沒有揮中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.81,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我肯定那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔把球打到鐵柱上發的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是事實並非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個聲音到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.18,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些火藥的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.97,0:14:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時橘經理打到的球就是這顆球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那個"鐺"的一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這顆球打到那根鐵柱發的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.98,0:14:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個裝了炸彈的球的碎片又是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是兇手使用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的兇手另有其人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之有話到局裏再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 得快點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 只有用老方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員警先生請你相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不是殺人兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的確不是殺人兇手 安井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追根究底那場爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.80,0:15:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由於被害人打到裝有炸彈的球所引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個想法是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.56,0:15:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發現場不是明明發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝上雷管的高爾夫球碎片了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 的確是有這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你看看這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顆球是我在圍網那裏的鐵柱下面找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己聞聞看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以聞到一點火藥味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 有火藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為炸彈爆炸的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘經理打的不是裝有炸彈的球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.21,0:16:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打的只是上面畫有藍線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是屬於練習場的球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先把話說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不懂你到底在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.93,0:16:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.39,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實並不是把裝了炸彈的球放進領球機裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是把炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.77,0:16:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先裝在長距離球桿的桿頭上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.73,0:16:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點就是這個兇手非常聰明的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道炸藥在打擊的那一瞬間會爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.53,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現場只要有被炸藥炸碎的球的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信每個人都會認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸的是被打中的那個高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以兇手就趁爆炸的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他事先裝好雷管的高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放置在案發的現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.29,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 會這麼做的兇手到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.59,0:17:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你今天曾經提過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理的長距離球桿的修理費用的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為球桿上面有裂痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以南智史就拿去修了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南智史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.68,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你把球桿送到哪裏去修理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.61,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裏也為客人修理球桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那修理的結果怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們換了一個新的球桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們原本是打算換上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.35,0:17:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前最流行的碳纖維球桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那根球桿是現在的社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十五年前送給我們經理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們經理非常喜歡那根球桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會讓球桿保持和從前一樣的木製頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那修理好的球桿什麼時候交給南先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是前天晚上交給他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天的晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你是到今天早上才拿給經理的 不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根球桿就等於有一天一夜的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南先生的手上了 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.00,0:18:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這就回想一下南先生你今天的整個行蹤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在到了這裏之後馬上就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你肚子痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這傢伙真是掃興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗手間 早去早回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.60,0:18:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他事先計畫好的行動當中的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平常打球的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會請南先生從領球機裏把球拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.07,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從這些球裏留下大概十個球倒進橘經理的球桶裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次他就是因為不想讓自己做這個工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.21,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會在一開始就佯裝肚子痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃到洗手間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來他為了要讓安井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉進圈套裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把爆炸的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.70,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,設定在你離開案發現場之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你幾乎每次在把長距離球桿交給橘經理之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會離開位子到櫃檯去幫他點咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他的目的就輕易達成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.70,0:19:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓自己完全擺脫殺人兇手的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在爆炸的那一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.30,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想到特地站到靠近案發現場旁邊的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.50,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你仔細看一下南先生身上受傷的部位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.50,0:19:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保先生幾乎全身都受到爆炸威力的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他卻只有左手的外側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及左腳膝蓋以下的部位受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏只有左邊受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且為什麼不是內側 而都是外側受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為 他在爆炸幾秒前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下意識地先用手遮住眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且又躲在柱子背後的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把再過不久就要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉任到紐約分公司去的橘經理給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下今天這個機會了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會利用這根從前天晚上到今天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在你手上的球桿當作兇器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.40,0:20:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這一點看來你的計畫似乎還有欠周詳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直很恨我們經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨他對我的才能始終不表示認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.00,0:20:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也恨整天就對部長阿諛奉承的安井課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就計畫殺了經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.60,0:20:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再設計陷害安井課長成為殺人兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成的結果很有可能會波及別人 難道你不在乎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果當時這個練習場有很多人受傷的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才管不了那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人所說的話全都是真心話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 那邊很危險 不可以靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.30,0:21:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他那時候對我說那些就是不想讓我受到波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他本來是個心地很好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知道什麼原因走了錯路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上學要遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.00,0:23:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.80,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.70,0:23:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二個星期天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔竟然白癡地答應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.50,0:23:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跟沖野洋子小姐同一組的條件之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起參加一場高爾夫名人大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.00,0:23:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐雖然打偏了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.60,0:23:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還算打得不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.30,0:23:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著我們請名偵探毛利小五郎先生露一手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.70,0:23:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.60,0:23:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他沒有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.50,0:23:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.70,0:23:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
